title: Josh Grabelle from Bullet Tooth/Trustkill Records
itunes:title: Josh Grabelle from Bullet Tooth/Trustkill Records
description:
In this episode we sit down with CEO of Bullet Tooth Records (previously known as Trustkill Records) Josh Grabelle and talk about his love for pop music, Israel and why labels are an easy scapegoat. We also chat about the new M83, Trash Talk, Four Year Strong and Paranormal Activity 3.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
